 <title>Playwriting Activity</title>
 <link>https://kennedyprize.columbia.edu/winners/2013/schenkkan/page/playwriting-activity-0</link>
 <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;This playwriting exercise for students developed by &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.youngplaywrights.org/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Young Playwrights Inc.&lt;/a&gt; uses monologue to explore and develop a compelling character.  This excercise has been adapted for use with this image of Roy Wilkins by presidential photographer Yoichi Okamoto.&lt;/p&gt;
