<item>
 <title>The History Behind the Scenes</title>
 <link>https://kennedyprize.columbia.edu/winners/2013/schenkkan/page/history-behind-scenes-1</link>
 <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-teaser field-type-text-long field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Learning from Historians&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;: &lt;/strong&gt;Scene 1, Activity 2&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Johnson was a pragmatic politician.  Sometimes his pursuit of political power and success stood at odds with his desire to improve the lives of America’s disadvantaged through legislation. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;i&gt;All The Way &lt;/i&gt;&lt;span&gt;highlights these conflicting impulses in Johnson’s character.  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Read these comments about Johnson from various historians and decide: &lt;strong&gt;w&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;i&gt;hat did Lyndon Johnson really want?&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;i&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/i&gt;Read:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/winners/2013/schenkkan/node/57&quot;&gt;Excerpt&lt;/a&gt; from Doris Kearns Goodwin&#039;s &lt;em&gt;Lyndon Johnson and the American Dream&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/winners/2013/schenkkan/node/62&quot;&gt;Excerpt&lt;/a&gt; from Robert Mann&#039;s &lt;i&gt;When Freedom Would Triumph:  The Civil Rights Struggle in Congress&lt;/i&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/winners/2013/schenkkan/node/66&quot;&gt;Excerpt&lt;/a&gt; from Tom Bryant&#039;s article in Oregon Shakespeare Festival&#039;s &lt;em&gt;Illuminations &lt;/em&gt;magazine&lt;/p&gt;
